oments</source><ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://osf.io/mszqj/?view_only=0daf10c02c984ead8929452edf44e550">https://osf.io/mszqj/?view_only=0daf10c02c984ead8929452edf44e550</ext-link><comment>OSF, mszqj</comment></element-citation></p></sec><supplementary-material><ext-link xlink:href="elife-59436-supp-v1.zip">Download zip</ext-link><p>Any figures and tables for this article are included in the PDF. The zip folder contains additional supplemental files.</p></supplementary-material></sec></back></article>